Darwin's Ruben Costa impersonated police officer to find his wife and child . 
 He came home from work to find his wife had left with his young son . 
 Costa called a taxi company, pretending to be a police officer searching for a woman who had abducted a child . 
 The taxi company were able to provide Costa with his wife's location . 
 Costa confronted his wife at the women's refuge where she had fled . 
 Costa was handed a suspended sentence for his 'devious' actions . 
 